Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.81,0:00:05.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia itu makhluk yang menakutkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.18,0:00:19.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka membunuh,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,merampas,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan merenggut kebebasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.91,0:00:32.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diberi tahu hal itu sejak kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata itu semua benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.61,0:00:42.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan tetapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misi kali ini apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membasmi babi hutan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.01,0:02:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wilayah manusia, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.71,0:02:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kakekmu tidak salah\Nmengira kita sebagai pesuruh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti dia salah sangka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah pasti.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.55,0:03:07.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian tidak punya harga diri\Nsebagai rakyat Kerajaan Elenoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terutama kau, Tessia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dinding Air.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang seperti mereka ada di mana-mana, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat mengganggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan diladeni.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak kedengaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kubilang, tidak perlu meladeni mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan meladeni siapa pun\Nyang mencari masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia, kau keren sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah tidak tahan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan naik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia, seperti yang kau tahu,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,tiga ras, yaitu elf, manusia, dan dwarf,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah berselisih untuk waktu yang lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan adanya aliansi tiga negara,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,perselisihan telah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.85,0:05:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, itu hanyalah perjanjian\Nyang dilakukan oleh ketiga negara.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rakyatnya masih saling berselisih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.61,0:05:27.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama kebencian tidak hilang\Ndari hati semua orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.21,0:05:30.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini belum bisa disebut aliansi\Nyang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi hal itu, Tessia,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau harus menjadi contoh bagi yang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kita terlalu sering diserang?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena elf itu harganya mahal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa akur itu sesuatu yang mustahil, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.89,0:06:01.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, tapi aku pikir\Nkita harus berjuang sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo kita jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa lebih baik\Nkita menyembunyikan telinga kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetap akan ketahuan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, seperti biasa saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan dibenci hanya karena kita elf.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kita pergi untuk menolong mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak mungkin terjadi, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak butuh bantuan dari elf!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga Wykes adalah keluarga\Nyang terkenal di Kerajaan Sapin.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.61,0:07:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai harus menerima kekuatan elf\Nyang merupakan musuh besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Elijah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.78,0:07:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau yang manusia\Nberurusan dengan keluarga dwarf?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa sebenarnya kau seorang dwarf?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga seorang elf, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terpenting bagi kami, keluarga Wykes,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah melahirkan penyihir yang kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi hal itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.31,0:07:37.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bersedia menerima elf yang secara\Nalami berbakat mengendalikan Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walaupun itu dari ras musuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.51,0:07:46.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lancang sekali kau\Nmenguping pembicaraan orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.94,0:07:53.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah mereka punya rencana tersendiri
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.11,0:07:57.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau sekadar keras kepala\Nmenghalalkan segala cara.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.51,0:08:03.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dengan kekuatan ini di Kerajaan Sapin...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku akan menjadi\Npenyihir terkuat di Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.41,0:08:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah tugas dari mereka\Nyang terlahir di keluarga Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, apa maksudmu dengan semangat?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.11,0:08:26.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, tujuanmu berbeda denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak masalah\Njika tidak menjadi yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misi selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan pergi cukup jauh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya akan menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik, kalian mengganggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana Beast yang muncul di desa...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada di mana mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia, kau sudah berjuang keras.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah reaksi yang normal dari mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita juga akan bertindak seperti itu\Njika manusia datang ke negara kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku pikir tidak ada salahnya\Nuntuk berbicara sedikit saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.71,0:09:15.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kena.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengenainya, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada perlu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Babi hutan itu datang dari arah timur.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah memberi tahu kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, kenapa kalian memberi tahu kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena semua orang kesulitan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian akan membasmi mereka, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan pada kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tadi aku berhasil mengenainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa elf itu lemah?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya sedikit lengah saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biasanya aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia adalah mainan kita berikutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku lupa siapa namanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tertarik dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terpenting adalah gelarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putri dari Kerajaan Elenoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk menghancurkan aliansi menjijikkan ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,kupikir dia sudah cukup, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, sepertinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menyediakan\Nhadiah untuk Tuan Putri.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan senang jika dia menyukainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhasil!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walaupun Mana Beast,\Nmereka hanyalah babi hutan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan musuh kita...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fei!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lengah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau melihatnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir tidak mempan terhadapnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di satu sisi, elf sangat mahir\Ndalam memanipulasi Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tubuh mereka lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, bagaimana kalau putri dari\Nkerajaanmu mati di wilayah negara musuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan rakyat elf pikirkan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sendiri yang bilang sihir tak mempan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vio!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.30,0:12:41.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bukan kau yang menolongku...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vio! Fei!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku setuju.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku melakukannya sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan keras kepala.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo mundur dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia punya ide?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.41,0:13:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pokoknya kau harus segera mundur\Njika dirasa tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelah sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.80,0:13:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, kejar aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar, kenapa aku harus\Nmelakukan peran seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aktivitas fisik seperti ini\Ndi luar keahlianku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vio, lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir tidak mempan, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhasil?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah kehabisan Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Staminaku juga sudah habis.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.55,0:14:59.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah "bodoh" itu terlalu kejam?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.96,0:15:08.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa harus melakukan sesuatu\Ndalam situasi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu Arthur...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia, tidak boleh!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan, Mana milikmu sudah habis!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Arthur memberitahuku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana-nya...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.61,0:16:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penguatan tubuh dengan Mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakitnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan melakukan hal\Nseperti seorang Augmenter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia lebih hebat dari yang kuduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus menyiapkan\NMana Beast yang lebih kuat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak akan jadi masalah bagi mereka\Nuntuk bilang terima kasih, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mengharapkan\Nsopan santun dari manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana menurutmu, Tessia?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.98,0:17:52.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang tahu pasti akan melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak Elf!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini rumah kalian?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.25,0:17:59.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rumah yang bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebelumnya orang lain menempati rumah ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang itu pindah ke tempat yang jauh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya mereka adalah\Norang-orang yang sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga kenal dengan\Norang yang sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti apa dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia adalah orang yang menjadi tujuanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berbahaya sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana keadaannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia berhasil menyelesaikannya tanpa terluka.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitukah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti yang diharapkan dari cucumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menyombongkannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dia memang diberkati\Ndengan teman-teman yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teman?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga mengenalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, dia...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.01,0:18:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan sedikit pertemuan,\Ndunia akan berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan diubah dengan tangan kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, 'kan, Cynthia?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, Virion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.95,0:19:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Fei akan kembali ke Xyrus.\NBagaimana denganmu, Vio?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau akan pulang ke Elenoir?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan lebih cepat jika kau\Nmenggunakan gerbang dari Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku pergi ke Xyrus juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalian bertemu dengan Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, apa yang kau katakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi ke Xyrus?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertemu dengan Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau kenal dengan Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?\NKarena aku bersama dengannya di Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kadang-kadang bertemu dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alice cantik sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka memberikanku\Nkudapan panggang sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus memberikan\Nsesuatu sebagai gantinya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eleanor juga imut sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Reynolds seorang Augmenter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.78,0:20:07.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Curang!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Curang katamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.51,0:20:11.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tidak bertemu dengan Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.01,0:20:14.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya aku tidak tahu\Ndi mana dia berada di Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.55,0:20:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang memberitahuku juga.\NKalian berdua curang!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini adalah rumah Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya kita bisa bertemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.15,0:20:41.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus kusapa bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Lama tidak bertemu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.61,0:20:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku kangen"?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku datang"?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.65,0:20:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Apa kau senang bisa bertemu lagi denganku?"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik yang mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada gunanya bingung.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi dan lihat langsung saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah ada perlu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada perlu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ada di mana, Arthur?
